lead_paragraph: Jamie Vardy is "something exceptional" who can play at any level and Leicester City have yet to see the best of the prolific striker who will have an "amazing career", according to former Foxes captain Matt Elliott.

headline.print_headline: Prolific Vardy Can Reach the Top, Says Elliott
headline.main: Prolific Vardy Can Reach the Top, Says Elliott
